body:
@annarev @martinwicke Hi, I hide `ApplyAdaMax` op, however API compatibility check still failed. And I run
```bash
    $ bazel build tensorflow/tools/api/tests:api_compatibility_test
    $ bazel-bin/tensorflow/tools/api/tests/api_compatibility_test \
          --update_goldens True
```
I found the failure seems unrelated.
